     <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 border-t border-gray-200">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-16">Why host or book with Wanderlust?</h2>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 text-center">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-brand">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Unmatched Safety</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Every user is verified and every stay is covered by our comprehensive $1M guarantee. Travel with absolute peace of mind.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-brand">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-headset text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">24/7 Global Support</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Our neighborhood experts are available around the clock to help you with booking, check-in, or any issues during your stay.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center mb-6 text-brand">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-gem text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Premium Quality</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">We curate our listings meticulously. From modern downtown lofts to cozy beachfront cottages, expect the best.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
 
    <section class="py-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 text-center">What our community says</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
                <div class="flex text-brand mb-4 text-sm">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">"The UI is incredibly smooth and finding a beachfront property for our weekend getaway was seamless. The booking process felt extremely premium."</p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gray-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-gray-500 font-bold">AK</div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Akash Kushwah</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Guest from India</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
                <div class="flex text-brand mb-4 text-sm">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mb-6 leading-relaxed">"As a host, the dashboard and listing management tools are top-tier. I've doubled my bookings since moving to Wanderlust."</p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1438761681033-6461ffad8d80?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=facearea&facepad=2&w=100&h=100&q=80" alt="Sarah" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full object-cover">
                    <div>
                        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Sarah Jenkins</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Superhost in Colorado</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 mb-20">
        <div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden h-[400px] flex items-center p-10 md:p-16">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600596542815-ffad4c1539a9?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2075&q=80" alt="Host your home" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-0">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900/90 to-transparent z-10"></div>
            
            <div class="relative z-20 max-w-lg">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Questions about hosting?</h2>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-200 mb-8">Ask a Superhost. Get free, one-on-one help from our most experienced community members.</p>
                <button class="bg-white text-gray-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Connect with a Superhost
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-gray-100 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-8">
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900">Support</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Help Center</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Safety information</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Cancellation options</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900">Hosting</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Wanderlust your home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">WanderCover for Hosts</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Community forum</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900">Wanderlust</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Newsroom</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">New features</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="hover:underline">Careers</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900">Follow Us</h4>
                <div class="flex gap-4 text-xl text-gray-800">
                    <a href="#" class="hover:text-brand transition"><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" class="hover:text-brand transition"><i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i></a>
                    <a href="#" class="hover:text-brand transition"><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-300 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
            <p>© 2026 Wanderlust Private Limited. All rights reserved.</p>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
                <a href="#" class="hover:underline">Privacy</a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:underline">Terms</a>
                <a href="#" class="hover:underline">Sitemap</a>
            </div>
